Package: com.iphone-farm.server
Name: iPhone Farm Screen Server
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64
Description: High-performance MJPEG/WebSocket screen streaming daemon for iPhone farms.
             Streams screen over WiFi/USB on port 7777.
             API: /stream (MJPEG), /screenshot (JPEG), /info (JSON)
Maintainer: Farm Tool
Author: Farm Tool
Section: Utilities
Priority: optional
Depends: firmware (>= 14.0)
